org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.linker

Class ManagedType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.linker.ManagedType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Lifecycle, FactoryStateListener

    public class ManagedType
extends Object
implements FactoryStateListener, Lifecycle
    This class is responsible to create the factory for a given type declaration. It also instructs the factories to create the instance for each instance declaration targeting the managed factory.
